    @startuml
    title User Authentication and Request Flow
    skinparam backgroundColor transparent
    skinparam shadowing false
    skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
    skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor User
participant "Identity Provider" as IdP
participant "AI Orchestrator" as Orchestrator
participant "Policy Decision Point" as PDP
participant "AI Agent Gateway" as Gateway
participant "AI Executor" as Executor
participant "Tool Adapter" as Tool
participant "Enterprise Resource" as Resource

User -> IdP : Sign in
IdP --> User : ID token / SSO assertion
User -> Orchestrator : AI request + token
Orchestrator -> Orchestrator : Validate identity and create execution context
Orchestrator -> PDP : Evaluate capability authorization
PDP --> Orchestrator : allow / deny / conditions
Orchestrator -> Gateway : Execution request + delegated identity
Gateway -> Executor : Scoped execution token
Executor -> Tool : Scoped tool token
Tool -> Resource : Authorized resource access
Resource --> Tool : Result
Tool --> Executor : Tool response
Executor --> Gateway : Execution result
Gateway --> Orchestrator : Normalized result
Orchestrator --> User : Final answer

    @enduml
